  <brief_title>Effect of Different Anesthetic Techniques for Isolated Systolic Hypertensive Patients of Abdominal Surgery on Postoperative Hospital Stay and Morbidity</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Different Anesthetic Techniques for Isolated Systolic Hypertensive Patients of Abdominal Surgery on Postoperative Hospital Stay and morbidity---a Prospective, Randomized Study</official_title>
